id: pm-gygna8
title: pm deps tree must remain bounded on cyclic deep relationship graphs
description: "During full-lineage orientation, pm deps pm-kr3t --format tree --json expanded until the process exhausted roughly 4 GB of memory. Tree rendering needs cycle-safe visitation, explicit node/depth/token bounds, and a compact truncation diagnostic so graph context remains safe for agents."
