acceptance_criteria: "Cyclic and multiply-linked graphs terminate without repeated unbounded expansion; Tree output honors explicit node, depth, and token bounds with deterministic truncation metadata; A regression fixture reproduces the deep richly-linked topology without touching the real tracker; CLI and SDK dependency projections retain parity for bounded results"
parent: pm-x85o
resolution: Fixed and verified
expected_result: "Dependency tree and graph projections terminate deterministically on cyclic or deep graphs under explicit, explainable budgets."
actual_result: Iterative bounded traversal reports depth/node/edge/token truncation with full and omitted totals; cyclic packed acceptance and regression tests passed.
